-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
how to create a desktop top Icon

sudo apt-get install python3-dev
pip install pyinstaller --user
pyinstaller main.py

.exe file is located in dist/main
rename CamperSystem

create a file called CamperSystem.desktop
put this code into it

[Desktop Entry]
Encoding=UTF-8
Version=1.0
Type=Application
Terminal=false
Exec=/home/eeddey/Desktop/Capstone/dist/main/CamperSystem
Name=CamperSystem
Icon=/home/eeddey/Desktop/Capstone/icons/faucet.png

------
save to desktop
right click on CamperSystem.desktop
go to properties
go to permissions tab
check "Allow executing file as program"

